text: Capstone Domain: Sycophancy Detection and Mitigation. The course builds toward detecting and mitigating AI sycophancy - when models optimize for user approval over truth.

Chapter 0, Section 2 (Optimization): Code example: # The complete feedback loop
for batch in dataloader:
    output = model(batch)           # Forward
    loss = loss_fn(output, target)  # Measure gap
    loss.backward()                 # Signal direction
    optimizer.step()                # Close gap
    optimizer.zero_grad()           # Reset
